latestPosts.caption:
Breakdown of my Welcome Lunch outfit 💙

This @gazalguptacouture piece was love at first sight! Picked by Varun actually!! The colour, the intricatly embroidered silver and gold threadwork and side cape style dupatta which was perfect for a mountain-top celebration!⛰️

Completed the look with timeless charm mother of pearl choker and earrings from @minerali_store 
And always comfortable @crimzonworld heels

For hair I got some charms and earrings to add that extra something from @westsidestores and that vision was magically achieved by @hairbybarkhaa 
MUA @makeupbychandanimalik 

#explore #wedding #bride #bridalinspiration

latestPosts.caption:
Sharing few glimpses of my Mehndi🫶🏻 Not very fond of Mehndi but I still wanted my mehndi to be more than pretty patterns — so we turned it into a memory map. A little giraffe magic from our favorite trip, and our Babu (who couldn’t be there on the big day) found his spot right on my arm. And of course always wanted to get married in the mountains. Because love isn’t just in the vows — it’s in the details that make your heart smile.
